messages.message: What do you do with WordPress?
Hey Brian, I work for a company called Codeable, we help businesses of all sizes solve their WP problems.
How much for a site like "Texas ski ranch" ? Looks like mostly static content, maybe a calendar tie in.
Sure let me take a peek, is this for a business of your own or someone you know?
He and I were talking about. I told him my price would be between 40-80k
He doesn't have a website currently that was just an example he gave me
Would you prefer to hire a team for this?

I think he would like something small. Looking at the Texas site it looks pretty simple functionally. I would give you this one for free if you want to connect with him you can leave me out of the loop. I have a side project already so I am busy but if this is something you want to do I will mention you to him. He said we could get together next week to talk.
Yeah man, I don't think this site is going to be too tricky at all. Happy to toss you a referral fee for it should it go through.
